data.description: Welcome to 3626 Camille Lane, where your next homestead is situated on a sprawling 1.4 acre property. This home offers not only a residence, but an invitation to a lifestyle brimming with comfort, space and endless potential. When you step into this welcoming home, you will find not just one, but two expansive family rooms, one adorned with a wood stove. The kitchen has been tuned up with white cabinets and stainless appliances. The primary bedroom that was once 2 separate bedrooms offers tons of space and room for a sitting area or an awesome walk in closet. Refinished bathroom has a walk-in bathtub for safety and comfort. 2nd bedroom offers tons of natural light. You'll enjoy the wood paneled laundry room that is attached to the bathroom all situated off the back patio making it a perfect mud room. Outside, your imagination can roam just as freely as your animals. With 1.4 acres of land offering about an acre of pasture with water shares, a garden area & shed for storage, the possibilities are endless.
